						<p><hi rend="bold">Date-lost</hi></p>						

						<p>Seems to register a provision made by Tirumalaiyaṉ Narasaiyaṉ and others for offerings to god on the day of Kārttigai, the star of Tirumaṅgai Āḻvār. The details of the date are lost.</p>						

